prodNameC: 免疫特 2500 第三代前列腺特異性抗原試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Third Generation PSA Bead Pack (L2UP12): 
Coated with monoclonal murine anti-PSA antibody.
Third generation PSA Reagent Wedge (L2UPA2):
11.5 mL of a protein buffer/serum matrix, with preservative. 11.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-PSA antibody in buffer.
Third Generation PSA Adjustors (LUPL, LUPH):
Two vials (Low and High), 3 mL each, of PSA in a serum matrix, with preservative.
